      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Create a new Node\n- if list is empty, set head to the new node\n- otherwise, traverse to the end and append the new node\n  - loop until the current nodes next is null\n  - set the current nodes next to the new node\n- increase the size of the list\n- update tail pointer if necessary",
      "fontSize": 74.39982096354359,
