    {
      "id": "R0C26BfC-hiTW3NIHxh96",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -15233.280828220175,
      "y": -17530.912719909542,
      "width": 1783.9759318033891,
      "height": 836.9979858398654,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c70p",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1330888518,
      "version": 4359,
      "versionNonce": 1413452122,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773458582074,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Approach 1: \n- convert linked list into array\n  - create an array\n  - traverse through each item of linked list\n  - push each item value into array\n  - calculate the length and find middle index\n  - return the subarray from the middle to end\n\n- S.C. -> 0(n), T.C. -> 0(n) ",
      "fontSize": 74.39982096354359,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Approach 1: \n- convert linked list into array\n  - create an array\n  - traverse through each item of linked list\n  - push each item value into array\n  - calculate the length and find middle index\n  - return the subarray from the middle to end\n\n- S.C. -> 0(n), T.C. -> 0(n) ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "B630JKkzpXeP7nb3eskb8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -17130.613998793095,
      "y": -17525.24489357491,
      "width": 1783.9759318033891,
      "height": 1115.9973144531536,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c70q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1822710214,
      "version": 4984,
      "versionNonce": 379347482,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773517631304,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Approach 2: fast & slow pointers\n- keep track of two pointers: fast && slow\n- initialize both pointers at head of linked list\n  - move each pointers one by one where slow\n    pointer moves one step at a time and fast\n    pointer takes 2 step. when fast pointer \n    reaches the end, slow pointer will be at the \n    middle.\n- when fast pointer reaches end of the list,\n  the slow pointer will be at the middle\n\n- T.C. -> 0(n), S.C. -> 0(1)",
      "fontSize": 74.39982096354359,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Approach 2: fast & slow pointers\n- keep track of two pointers: fast && slow\n- initialize both pointers at head of linked list\n  - move each pointers one by one where slow\n    pointer moves one step at a time and fast\n    pointer takes 2 step. when fast pointer \n    reaches the end, slow pointer will be at the \n    middle.\n- when fast pointer reaches end of the list,\n  the slow pointer will be at the middle\n\n- T.C. -> 0(n), S.C. -> 0(1)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "pCtlrFLnxQLisk0kSra0P",
